data.description: This home has an open concept family room with Kitchen/dining room combination and first floor laundry. There is a breakfasr bar with tall cabinets and a dine in area with bay window.There are barrel rolled ceilings in family and dining room.There is an elevated deck overlooking a wooded nature area with privacy from neighbors, and a partially exposed lower level ready to be finished to double the living space. There is a rough in already for a third bath in the lower level. Close and convenient to any and everything- I90/Riverside interchange. This one will not last long!
